---
title: Bacon and Broccoli Stir-Fry with Green Onion Rice
description: Low on time, big on flavour, our Bacon and Broccoli Stir-Fry is sure to be a hit with the family! Crispy bacon is wonderful, of course, but the soy-garlic broccoli and sugar snap peas truly shine in this stir-fry. Cover it all in a flavour-packed hoisin-sweet chili sauce and this may just be the easiest way to dish out vegetables for dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-and-broccoli-stir-fry-64c54990.jpg
